flowchart TB
    subgraph CLIENT_DEVICE[User Device]
        BROWSER[Chrome Browser]
        EXT[Vaultword Extension]
        LOCAL[(Browser Local Storage)]
    end

    subgraph HOST_MACHINE[Local Host Machine]
        API[Node.js Express API Server]
        DB[(SQLite Database File)]
        ENV[Environment Configuration]
    end

    USER[User] --> BROWSER
    BROWSER --> EXT
    EXT --> LOCAL

    EXT -->|HTTP on localhost:3000| API
    API --> DB
    API --> ENV

    EXT -->|JWT Authorization Header| API
    EXT -->|Encrypted credential payload| API
